=== Diamonds agreed and we are at the 4-level

If diamonds were _reaffirmed_ as per the previous section, then 4H is
kickback.

If hearts were bid on the first round, then hearts are in focus and 4H
is an offer to play, usually showing honour doubleton.

If 4H is not kickback then 4S will be kickback unless spades were also
bid on the first round.

If neither 4H nor 4S is kickback, then [lavender-bg]#4NT is KC asking
for {D}#.

