=== ConFit

CAUTION: Replaces Gerber

Applies after: +
@ 1NT opening
@ Mexican 2D opening
@ 2NT family openings +
@ nebulous 2C (2/1) then 2NT rebid by
_  either showing 15{OrMore}-17 & no singleton

Used with balanced or semi-balanced hands when
[nobr]#minimum total HCP = 32{ndash}33#

The asking bid is a jump to 4C opposite a balanced or semi-balanced hand
of 1NT opening-strength or greater.

The TELLER (usually opener) shows control points (A=2, K=1), then we seek a fit.

The number of control points shown by the first step, depends on the
point range shown by the limited hand.

